    - Each version viewable in read-only mode
    - Timeline shows evolution. Search shows existence.

RESULTS MERGING
    - All result types combined into single list
    - Deduplication by UUID (newest version shown)
    - Chronological sorting (most recent first)
    - Pagination adapts to terminal height
    - Numbered selection works identically for all types

SEARCH DOES NOT DISTINGUISH
    - Between current, deleted, or renamed
    - Between notes, files, or notebooks
    - Between locations or notebooks
    - All writing is equally findable. All time is equally present.

